    cat: "ai",
    title: "Paramount Plus is two dollars for two months of ad-free viewing",
    summary: "Paramount Plus is offering new and former subscribers a discounted rate until June 25th, 2026. You’ll pay 99 cents per month for the first two months, with the Premium plan automatically renewing for $13.99 per month after that, and the more limited Essential plan renewing for $8.99.&#160; Both plans include some excellent shows, like Freaks [&#8230;]",
    body: "A poster showing the cast of Star Trek: Strange New Worlds | Image: Paramount Paramount Plus is offering new and former subscribers a discounted rate until June 25th, 2026. You’ll pay 99 cents per month for the first two months, with the Premium plan automatically renewing for $13.99 per month after that, and the more limited Essential plan renewing for $8.99.&nbsp; Paramount Plus (two months) Now through June 25th, new and former subscribers can get a two-month subscription to Paramount Plus Essential (ad-supported) or Paramount Plus Premium (ad-free) for 99 cents per month.\n\nThe deal saves you over $20 and includes access to a catalog of over 40,000 TV shows and movies, including Star Trek: Strange New Worlds, The Naked Gun, South Park, and The Daily Show. Where to Buy: $8.99 $0.99 at Paramount Plus Essential (two months) $13.99 $0.99 at Paramount Plus Premium (two months) Both plans include some excellent shows, like Freaks and Geeks , Colin from Accounts , and South Park, and is one of the only places to find the majority of the Star Trek series — I know I’ll be spending two dollars to rewatch The Next Generation .\n\nYou can also find new movies like the 2025 Naked Gun reboot, classics like Mean Girls , while both plans include access to live NFL games on CBS, UEFA Champions League matches, and Showtime Originals. The Essential plan only includes a subset of the Showtime Originals found on the Premium plan, is ad supported, and doesn’t allow for downloads or live CBS. window.HYPE_DESK_CONFIG = { productImageUrl: \"https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/06/image1.png\", productImageAlt: \"CORSAIR Xeneon Edge LCD Touchscreen\", productTitle: \"CORSAIR Xeneon Edge LCD Touchscreen\", shortDescription: \"A second screen that actually earns its spot on your desk.\", longDescription: \"Your main monitor handles the heavy lifting.\n\nThe Xeneon Edge handles everything else. The Xeneon Edge is a 14.5-inch ultrawide touchscreen that magnetically attaches to your case, PSU shroud, desk, or stand, giving you a dedicated dashboard for system stats, widgets, chat, shortcuts, and more. With new iCUE widgets and community-created layouts, it gets more useful over time. Use code XENEON30 for $30 off.\", purchaseUrl: \"https://go.corsair.com/c/482924/490888/8513?subId1=VergeHypedeskAricle4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corsair.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fp%2Fmonitors%2Fcc-9011306-ww%2Fxeneon-edge-14-5-lcd-touchscreen-cc-9011306-ww&amp;partnerpropertyid=7032191\", purchaseLinkText: \"Shop at Corsair\" };",
