    summary: "On this episode of Stock Movers with Alexis Christoforous: - La-Z-Boy (LZB) shares are higher after the home furniture store’s reported adjusted earnings per share for the fourth quarter beat the average analyst estimate. - CarMax (KMX) shares are moving after it reported net sales & operating revenue for the first quarter that beat the average analyst estimate. - Jabil Inc. (JBL) shares rose as…",
